{"tid":1065741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔撚注意[南亞借錢黨]","createTime":"2019-03-17T12:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T13:36:32.000Z","uid":31426,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9424183ed997b03efa6974963ef5dee4e1db89d0","tid":1065741,"uid":31426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T12:54:43.000Z","msg":"大埔太和 [南亞仔借錢黨] 17-3-2019 (19:00)<br />\n<br />\n起太和社區中心出面撞到個南亞仔, 身高約170, 識講南亞口音英文<br />\n起始時用英文, 報稱黎香港兩日但被偷行李, 要求借宿兩天+借錢買M記+搭車<br />\n本人多次建議送佢去警署+致電999(本來想送佢去社區中心, 但岩岩好關門休息)<br />\n但被拒絕, 並強調只要少少錢就可以<br />\n本人揭發後即刻想向太和巴士站方向逃走, 我隨後上前追問<br />\n煩到佢終於認錯, 話自己講大話, 求我放過佢, 但我繼續追問<br />\n佢最後起巴士站執起木板並且發難, 作勢要打我, 我大聲呼叫後, 佢就即刻跑走<br />\n隨後已經向大廈看更備案, 要求出通知<br />\nP.S.唔好問我點解無拍片/叫幫手<br />\n一來 我拎電話佢已經想走<br />\n二來 同佢理論時已經開始想打我趕走我,當時自保優先都諗唔到好多野 <br />\n三來 無路人幫手是常識吧<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DBoEG7m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDBoEG7m.png&h=2de6a2b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v6qchFJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv6qchFJ.png&h=3c2eab49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fHOxhFK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfHOxhFK.png&h=a6eb411a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家出街小心D, 尤其係女仔, 下次可能唔止借錢咁簡單"},{"pid":"da1bd21bbe9f8e7ad70c973d3c25d5d7992fe926","tid":1065741,"uid":165510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:00:30.000Z","msg":"有排喺大元邨嗰邊近巴士總站好似見過佢同另外幾隻蝻<br />\n好熟面口"},{"pid":"35cedb24e7357244b6df39fdb32fec712c11ceea","tid":1065741,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:01:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdcb95fed8a552b007835944aeee7288e165e121","tid":1065741,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:05:34.000Z","msg":"有個肥仔南亞成日係tuen mum站搵食, 要人比100$佢, 又係唔見哂d野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03838f375b8e139ecb31ef001d911f2a6f633bab","tid":1065741,"uid":237611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:06:56.000Z","msg":"隻南亞狗好似有靚錶係手啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223a6edc5a45840b9aaee75b24d530062c8619a7","tid":1065741,"uid":148332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:21:18.000Z","msg":"佢地屈機之處在於認唔到樣"},{"pid":"48d6ee9ba51c38fc33029d7f3da7cfca870ca753","tid":1065741,"uid":41508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:34:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db5b970627914a0d14afbc8b242ec5b6c143bed6","tid":1065741,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T13:36:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}